main event: Photographs of an unidentified aerial object or phenomenon were taken in Coolville, Ohio in January 1969.
interesting points: The photographs show a dark, blurry object against a hazy background.
There are no human faces or identities visible in the images.
The images contain blurred, indistinct shapes that seem to be some sort of unidentified aerial phenomena.
One of the images is a grainy, black and white photograph or scan with no clear visual content or identifiable subject matter.
The report is associated with Project Blue Book, a historical U.S. Air Force program that investigated UFO sightings.
